raight up in the air. What I find interesting is that the p', 'Get a concise weekly outlook on crude oil, gold, forex pairs, and NASDAQ 100, with key levels and market drivers to watch.', 'weekly-pairs-in-focus-may-04-may-10-2025-charts', 'General', 'Broker Analysis', NULL, 'published', '2025-08-21T13:03:44.298675', 'C:\Users\LENOVO\Desktop\BrokeranalysisDaily\daily forex\www.dailyforex.com\forex-technical-analysis\2025\05\pairs-in-focus-this-week-may-4th-to-may-10th-2025\227794.html', 'Get a concise weekly outlook on crude oil, gold, forex pairs, and NASDAQ 100, with key levels and market drivers to watch.'),
